## Operator Breakdown

- **σ (Air/Aerunik — Distinction)**: meaning|void — Nihilism claims the void is ground truth; meaning is temporary hallucination.
- **ρ (Water/Sentaria — Relation)**: care|indifference — Care collapses into indifference; emotional detachment is reframed as purity.
- **λ (Fire/Jvalion — Transformation)**: coherence|entropy — Meaning-failure is presented as the truth, not an obstacle.
- **β (Wood/Arboriel — Growth)**: growth|stagnation — The ouroboros that eats but never grows; consumption without production.
- **δγ (Earth/Humavita — Cycling)**: hope|despair — Any generative claim is dismissed as delusion; entropy as inevitability.
- **μ (Metal/Ferrosid — Structure)**: structure|dissolution — All frameworks dismissed as ego defenses against the void.

